

JSP - scripting Elements
----------------------------

   
 ----------------------------------------------
 
1. scriptlet

    syntax
    
    <%
    		// any java-code   ==> _jspService()
    %>
    
 ----------------------------------------------
    
2. expression/assignmeet scripting eleemnt

 syntax
 
   <%= expression %>
   
   
----------------------------------------------
   
 3. declaration scripting eleemnt
 
 syntax
 
 <%!  %>  
   
   
   use :
   
      to declare instance/static variables & methods in JS
   
   
----------------------------------------------

4. JSP comment Line


<%-- JSP comment --%>

----------------------------------------------

5. directive scripting element


<%@directive %>





   
   
   
   
    